The  "string param" comment on the indexer parameter is being discarded in this test case
https://typescript.codeplex.com/SourceControl/latest#tests/cases/compiler/commentsInterface.ts

```typescript
    /** this is indexer*/
    [/**string param*/i: string]: any;
```

This produces in the commentsInterface.js baseline

```typescript
    /** this is indexer*/
    [i: string]: any;
```

( I have a local fix.  can submit PR. )
